name: Health and wealth of nations
body:
# Health and Wealth of Nations

###This is a brief exercise of using d3.js for data visualization, a partial recreation of gap minders health and wealth of nations, and Mike Bostock's d3 version. (I can only stand in awe of their work)

###Data was taken from the [World Bank](http://data.worldbank.org/) website
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
